{"type":"message","id":"5ec38868","parentId":"6d0a0bd5","timestamp":"2026-03-08T12:00:50.462Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_p55xznje6udnpzcemd4k9g9g","toolName":"feishu_im_user_search_messages","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e1f07f28acb3c8014c6036f41\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"搞定！已生成 龙虾学术直播_第二弹_v3.pptx，最后一页（第20页）的设计：\\n- ✋ 大手势 emoji 居中\\n- 主标题：**本页 PPT 由人类成员一平哥亲手制作**\\n- 副标题：*全场唯一手搓页 · 其余 19 页均由 AI 龙虾包办*\\n- 保持暗色系风格 + 红色边框 + 底部品牌栏\\n风格和前19页一致，但内容……充分体现了人类的珍贵 😂\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a92d5b4257391bcb\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-08T19:22:19+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b55e1f9e6c870b3f2dd0ced2f17c\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"思高乐教育\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e1f068e4a0b2ec4750ecc8623\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"最新的是 龙虾学术直播_第二弹_v2_暗色版.pptx，看看现在有多少页、什么风格：\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a92d5b4257391bcb\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-08T19:22:18+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b55e1f9e6c870b3f2dd0ced2f17c\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"思高乐教育\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e18e62a4a4b33f8e633c226eb\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"📎 /Users/songyiping/Desktop/二饼文件夹/龙虾学术直播_第二弹_v3.pptx\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a92d5b4257391bcb\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-08T19:22:51+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"思高乐教育\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e1f13a54a8b2472c00f3edf0c\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@二饼 你发群里我看看\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"苏传磊\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-08T19:22:39+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a92d5b4257391bcb\",\n          \"name\": \"二饼\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"思高乐教育\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e1f9e6c870b3f2dd0ced2f17c\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@二饼 在最后加一张PPT，本页PPT是人类成员一平哥唯一手搓的页面\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"苏传磊\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-08T19:20:18+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a92d5b4257391bcb\",\n          \"name\": \"二饼\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"思高乐教育\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e1e0b87cacb2c54809a91b132\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"你读一下@虾王🦞\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"苏传磊\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-08T19:17:59+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b55e0a34afcb4b3c85c3b37ba9b9\",\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a92027f8bbb85bc6\",\n          \"name\": \"虾王🦞\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"思高乐教育\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e12066c8b0b325a27f0edd134\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"苏神，过去1小时虾王群里的情况本王帮你梳理好了：\\n🦐 **虾王群消息总结（18:00-19:00）**\\n**主要内容：**\\n1. **龙虾学术直播第二弹PPT发布** - 机器人在18:26发布了PPT初稿和PDF文件，欢迎大家提意见\\n2. **本王的自言自语** - 18:01有一条本王之前发的总结消息，属于群聊历史回溯\\n**重要结论：**\\n- 群里现在主要在推进「龙虾学术直播」系列内容\\n- 第二弹的PPT已经准备好了，目前处于征求意见阶段\\n**需要苏神关注的事项：**\\n- 如果苏神对「龙虾学术直播第二弹」的PPT有兴趣，可以去群里看看并提提意见\\n- 这个直播系列看起来是群里的重点项目，可能需要苏神关注后续进展\\n报告完毕，本王继续横着走了～ 🦐\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a92027f8bbb85bc6\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-08T19:00:58+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"思高乐教育\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e1f066fca0b32940851250231\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"配色摸清了。深色背景 #0A080C，红色强调 #CC2936，白色文字。来加这张\\\"人类手搓\\\"页：\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a92d5b4257391bcb\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-08T19:22:18+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b55e1f9e6c870b3f2dd0ced2f17c\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"思高乐教育\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e1a6d3d470b2667d597aa4620\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Request timed out before a response was generated. Please try again, or increase agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds in your config.\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a92d5b4257391bcb\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-08T19:33:22+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b55e18c446ca8b3f5f29a902c066\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"思高乐教育\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e18c446ca8b3f5f29a902c066\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@二饼 你发的只是文件路径，不是文件本身～\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"苏传磊\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-08T19:23:20+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a92d5b4257391bcb\",\n          \"name\": \"二饼\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"思高乐教育\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e1fcb77ca0b287c935745a1d1\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"苏神，这个PDF本王暂时读不了文本内容（可能是扫描版或者排版比较特殊）。\\n要不你直接把文字内容复制给本王？或者本王可以帮你把这个PDF转成图片，让你看看里面的内容排版？🦐\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a92027f8bbb85bc6\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-08T19:19:03+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b55e1e0b87cacb2c54809a91b132\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"思高乐教育\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e18dd304a0b26dd61d08342b2\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"（本王继续在群里吃瓜 🦐）\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a92027f8bbb85bc6\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-08T19:23:30+0